53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛教其實要有理論同實踐<br />\n只停留係理論上只會成為文化學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔會令你有得著</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，信解行證係一步步<br />\n不過唔洗好似返團契咁，睇啱先再深入了解，唔啱就算，無所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96f4de68c054efd448d1869ebd444c059edea33","tid":425159,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先學咩係緣份，明白緣之後學其他野好簡單</blockquote><br />\n之前有特登search過緣呢樣野，但諗到成個宇宙觀就覺得好似有少少解唔通"},{"pid":"968f7770f1681f6d13793947a163aab48fbe6568","tid":425159,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛教其實要有理論同實踐<br />\n只停留係理論上只會成為文化學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔會令你有得著</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誠然，小弟冇乜信心可以跟到佛學入面咁對任何塵俗嘅事都大徹大悟，但會盡量去透過理解而明白，之前慢慢實踐"},{"pid":"5b8cf0f0d735490ab15a2454868d8f30e2fde728","tid":425159,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> tg: Eulerlagrangian"},{"pid":"31533d2aa4b49ea7e1e14faf458a0fd176feca16","tid":425159,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀 方便留一留嗎 我有個朋友都想學下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfff33fb7eff514cfe5d64c8e607e5a5414c0fd","tid":425159,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佛教其實要有理論同實踐<br />\n只停留係理論上只會成為文化學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔會令你有得著</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，信解行證係一步步<br />\n不過唔洗好似返團契咁，睇啱先再深入了解，唔啱就算，無所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學佛本來就係輕鬆自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係怕樓主誤睇戒律睇到自我封閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4e7ca78ff1fb6c0b56e2e0a5c17df12180ec78","tid":425159,"uid":43842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佛教其實要有理論同實踐<br />\n只停留係理論上只會成為文化學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔會令你有得著</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誠然，小弟冇乜信心可以跟到佛學入面咁對任何塵俗嘅事都大徹大悟，但會盡量去透過理解而明白，之前慢慢實踐</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔好誤會 學佛其實係一件好貼地既事黎<br />\n而家既你係人 唔係佛陀 唔洗諗到咁抽身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要做好自己身為人既本分先 你先會明佛教其實搞乜<br />\n<br />\n何況佛陀都會有鬧鳩人既時候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當然唔係亂鬧<br />\n(詳情請睇&quot;阿含經內 久離恐怖的佛陀&quot;)"},{"pid":"8dadb7258b491fc1e7cbaeea985bd0a023b361c6","tid":425159,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佛教其實要有理論同實踐<br />\n只停留係理論上只會成為文化學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔會令你有得著</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，信解行證係一步步<br />\n不過唔洗好似返團契咁，睇啱先再深入了解，唔啱就算，無所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學佛本來就係輕鬆自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係怕樓主誤睇戒律睇到自我封閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呢層當然唔會啦，原本係略略鑽研下哲學，之後對佛學都產生咗少少興趣，所以就開po問下，想從佛學方面睇下個世界觀"},{"pid":"be0b5e91824ec8998ea847257b9e7feac6452727","tid":425159,"uid":139077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b